      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "LTX Desktop collects minimal, anonymous usage analytics (app version, platform, and a random installation ID) to help prioritize development. No personal information or generated content is collected. Analytics is enabled by default and can be disabled in **Settings > General > Anonymous Analytics**. See [`TELEMETRY.md`](docs/TELEMETRY.md) for details."
    },
