      "z_value": -9.934000000000037,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "## Contributing"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Practical and pleasurable",
      "uuid": "64f54632fff14868a2673e790faa6604",
      "x": 10961.786895169118,
      "y": 4991.33561494949,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 326.0,
      "z_value": -9.954000000000025,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "```mermaid\ngraph TD\n  UI[\"Renderer (React + TS)\"] -->|HTTP: localhost:8000| BE[\"Backend (FastAPI + Python)\"]\n  UI -->|IPC via preload: window.electronAPI| EL[\"Electron main (TS)\"]\n  EL --> OS[\"OS integration (files, dialogs, ffmpeg, process mgmt)\"]\n  BE --> GPU[\"Local models + GPU (when supported)\"]\n  BE --> EXT[\"External APIs (only for API-backed features)\"]\n  EL --> DATA[\"App data folder (settings/models/logs)\"]\n  BE --> DATA\n```"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Becoming Yours",
      "uuid": "af890d1ed4bb40fd88982bd9e0866256",
      "x": 10126.343780112507,
      "y": 4226.992375009858,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.957000000000024,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "## Architecture"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "All Glory",
      "uuid": "02b7dcec5de64eec85753488502fe075",
      "x": 10622.538350005992,
      "y": 4689.424454994739,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 356.0,
      "z_value": -9.955000000000025,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "- **Renderer (`frontend/`)**: TypeScript + React UI.\n  - Calls the local backend over HTTP at `http://localhost:8000`.\n  - Talks to Electron via the preload bridge (`window.electronAPI`).\n- **Electron (`electron/`)**: TypeScript main process + preload.\n  - Owns app lifecycle and OS integration (file dialogs, native export via ffmpeg, starting/managing the Python backend).\n  - Security: renderer is sandboxed (`contextIsolation: true`, `nodeIntegration: false`).\n- **Backend (`backend/`)**: Python + FastAPI local server.\n  - Orchestrates generation, model downloads, and GPU execution.\n  - Calls external APIs only when API-backed features are used."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Inner Peace",
      "uuid": "44c59f228f47467ca088c6f3bad4386e",
      "x": 10387.541292832477,
      "y": 4397.950908211853,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
